  m_text: "Each course object has a few settings\n\n- Par/Max Score\n- Par/Max Time\n-
    Driving Range Mode\n- Can the course be played after completion again\n- Short/Long
    name of course\n- References to:\n    - Ball spawn positions\n    - Hole colliders
    (you can have more than one!)\n    - Floor colliders \n           (!! Make sure
    to assign your floor colliders for each course !!)"
